snippet.title: Steve Lehto
snippet.description:
I am a Michigan attorney who has practiced in the fields of Lemon Law and Consumer Protection for 30 years. I have written extensively on a variety of topics and taught both law and history. My videos and podcasts are the reincarnation of the talk show I hosted for a decade called "Lehto's Law." I have also written books on a variety of topics, often involving cars and Michigan history.

For Lehto's Law T-Shirts, visit: https://www.zazzle.com/store/lehtoslaw
Send story ideas to steve@lehtoslaw.com

If you wish to send correspondence to me via the US Postal service, please use this address:

P.O. Box 168
Atlas MI 48411

Website: http://www.lehtoslaw.com
